<refnamediv><refname>imremap</refname><refpurpose>Remap an image using x/y coordinate maps.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>imout = imremap(imin, mapx, mapy, method)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>imremap</function> is a macro implementation of nearest-neighbor coordinate remapping.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
im = uint8([1 2; 3 4]);
out = imremap(im, [1 2; 1 2], [1 1; 2 2]);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
